name: retrieval
description: A tool that queries the knowledge retrieval API to get an answer to a query from ingested documents. Response contains also source references that can be used for citations.
args: knowledge_retrieval_api_url: The URL of the Knowledge Retrieval API to send the query to.
args: dataset: The name of the dataset which is expected to hold the answer.
args: prompt: The query prompt to ask the vector database. URL Encoded string.

#!http://${knowledge_retrieval_api_url}/datasets/${dataset}/query?query=${prompt}&topk=5
